snippet.title: Jaaneman Title song (Bengali) (2012)

localized.description:
Here's presenting the title song of Jaaneman which stars Soham and Koel. This song has been composed by Jeet Gannguli and sung by Jeet Gannguli and Shilpa Rao.

Film : Jaaneman 
Starring : Sohom, Koel Mallick
Producer : Shree Venkatesh Films and Surinder Films
Director: Raja Chanda
Music: Jeet Ganguly
Singer : Jeet Ganguly & Shilpa Rao
Lyrics : Raja Chanda
